---
<Layout title="Priority Notices in Queensland Property Transactions: What Sellers Should Know | Daniel Gierach Property" description="A priority notice is a routine but misunderstood part of Queensland conveyancing. Here is what it means for sellers, what you can and cannot do once one is lodged, and how it resolves at settlement." draft={draft}>

